        {
            "title": "不讓AI專美於前！復華金融股債雙收傘型基金 瞄準歐美日巨頭",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UilYWltXkl3rqYYDPV0KQg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/6768a99d7ccc61058264bb373510ef8f\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
